data.description: Welcome to your renovated 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom  With bamboo flooring throughout, the main floor boasts a spacious kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample storage. Enjoy a dining room, living room, TV room, bedroom, and studio. Upstairs, find two large bedrooms and a bathroom. The finished basement offers a bathroom, laundry room, storage, and a versatile open space. Outside, a fenced front yard with a concrete patio and a tree house await. Privacy and modern comfort await in this hidden gem!
